# {{PROJECT_NAME}} 🚀

> Modern Electron desktop application with FBCA architecture, UIKit frontend, and AppKit backend

A cross-platform desktop application built with Electron, featuring Feature-Based Component Architecture on both frontend and backend, comprehensive UI components from UIKit, and powerful backend modules from AppKit.

---

## ✨ Features

### 🖥️ Desktop Application
- **Electron Desktop App** - Cross-platform (macOS, Windows, Linux)
- **Native Integration** - File system, OS dialogs, system tray
- **Offline-First** - Works without internet connection

### 🏗️ Architecture
- **FBCA Frontend** - React with auto-discovery routing
- **FBCA Backend** - Express with auto-discovery API routes
- **UIKit Components** - 37+ production-ready components
- **AppKit Modules** - 12 backend modules (auth, logger, error, etc.)

### 🎨 UI/UX
- **5 Professional Themes** - Base, Elegant, Metro, Studio, Vivid
- **Light/Dark Mode** - Automatic theme switching
- **Semantic Colors** - OKLCH color system with theme adaptation
- **Responsive Layouts** - Page layouts with UIKit

