## 🎨 Theme Customization

Change theme in `src/desktop/renderer/App.tsx`:

```tsx
<ThemeProvider theme="elegant" mode="light" forceConfig={true}>
  <App />
</ThemeProvider>
```

**Available themes:** `base` | `elegant` | `metro` | `studio` | `vivid`
**Available modes:** `light` | `dark`

