## 📝 Adding Features

### Frontend Feature

```bash
# 1. Create feature structure
mkdir -p src/desktop/renderer/features/products/pages
mkdir -p src/desktop/renderer/features/products/components

# 2. Create page (auto-route: /products)
# File: features/products/pages/index.tsx
```

```tsx
import { PageLayout } from '@voilajsx/uikit/page';

export default function ProductsPage() {
  return (
    <PageLayout>
      <PageLayout.Content>
        <h1 className="text-foreground">Products</h1>
      </PageLayout.Content>
    </PageLayout>
  );
}
```

**Done!** Route `/products` automatically available.

### Backend Feature

```bash
# 1. Create route file
mkdir -p src/desktop/main/features/products
# File: features/products/products.route.ts
```

```typescript
import { Router } from 'express';
import { errorClass } from '@voilajsx/appkit/error';

const router = Router();
const error = errorClass.get();

router.get('/', error.asyncRoute(async (req, res) => {
  res.json({ products: [] });
}));

export default router;
```

**Done!** Endpoint `/api/products` automatically available.

